Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/d-lord/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Adding submodules:
    git submodule init
    git submodule add [https://github.com/mikewest/vimroom] [bundle/vimroom]

Updating submodules and third-party dependencies:
    git submodule update --init --recursive
